## Describes what to do with rows that are too short for the specified
   fixed-width layout.
type Invalid_Fixed_Width_Rows
    ## Discards rows that are too short for the specified fixed-width layout.
    Drop_Invalid_Rows

    ## Keeps rows that are too short for the specified fixed-width layout,
       keeping partial columns, or using empty strings for entirely missing
       columns.
    Keep_Invalid_Rows
